Class FSAuthnResponse

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.identity.saml.protocol.AbstractResponse
      com.sun.identity.saml.protocol.Response
          com.sun.identity.federation.message.FSAuthnResponse

public class FSAuthnResponse
extends Response

The class FSAuthnResponse creates and parses the Liberty Response. This class extends the SAML Response.
